
          ZapDesc, a syntax colouring mode for Acorn DDE 'Desc' files
          ===========================================================

This mode has no documentation of its own, (apart from this file).

This mode shares a number of features with the Obey mode and you are
referred to this as a source of relevant documentation.

Although the author welcomes correspondence concerning this mode, he makes no
claim that it is bug free and, it is not guaranteed to perform any particular
function.  It is to be used entirely at one's own risk.

The module if Freeware, and may be distributed freely provided that all files
remain intact.

This file last updated 20-Jun-1997.

Enjoy
